      android:usesCleartextTraffic="true"), prefer one of these approaches:
        1) Add the attribute in the main AndroidManifest.xml and list it in tools:replace there,
           e.g. tools:replace="android:appComponentFactory,android:usesCleartextTraffic"
        2) Use a debug manifest with a single <application> and tools:node="replace" but
           be careful â€” that completely replaces the main <application> block.
    -->

</manifest>
